## DESCRIPTION
##   Modular Arithmetic
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## Tagged by nhamblet

## DBsubject(Number theory)
## DBchapter(Congruences)
## DBsection(Chinese remainder theorem)
## Institution(Rochester)
## Level(3)
